IMPORT JAVA.UTIL.OBJECTS;L;PUBLIC CLASS CHISLO {    PRIVATE DOUBLE CH1;    PUBLIC CHISLO(DOUBLE CH1){        THIS.CH1 = CH1;    }    PUBLIC DOUBLE GETCH1() {        RETURN CH1;    }    PUBLIC VOID SETCH1(DOUBLE CH1) {        THIS.CH1 = CH1;    }    @OVERRIDE    PUBLIC BOOLEAN EQUALS(OBJECT O) {        IF (THIS == O) RETURN TRUE;        IF (!(O INSTANCEOF CHISLO CHISLO)) RETURN FALSE;        RETURN DOUBLE.COMPARE(CHISLO.GETCH1(), GETCH1()) == 0;    }    @OVERRIDE    PUBLIC INT HASHCODE() {        RETURN OBJECTS.HASH(GETCH1());    }    @OVERRIDE    PUBLIC STRING TOSTRING() {        RETURN "CHISLO{" +                "CH1=" + CH1 +                '}';    }
